rem  THIS BAT FILE CAN BE COPIED TO YOUR HOME DIRECTORY ON
rem  THE C DISK OR WHATEVER. IT WILL CALL THE TRANSLATOR
rem  AND INTERPRETOR IN THE `a:\p_pascal' DIRECTORY.  ALSO
rem  YOU ONLY NEED SPECIFY THE NAME OF THE SOURCE PASCAL
rem  FILE WITH ITS DIRECTORY AND DRIVE, AND without THE
rem  `.pas' EXTENSION REQUIRED BY A COMMAND LINE CALL.
a:\p_pascal\translat %1.pas %1.pcd
a:\p_pascal\interpre %1.pcd
erase %1.pcd
